&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The Associate Directors and Directors of Account Strategy at 10up are responsible for owning and driving strategic partnerships for a set of diverse, cross-industry client portfolios or a sizable pillar account spanning multiple departments and work streams. Directors work closely with project teams to foster client success and growth through creative thinking, consistently exceptional delivery, and outstanding service.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As an Account Strategy leader you’ll have ownership and autonomy across a combination of innovative, challenging projects and ongoing support engagements. Client portfolios span from startups and impactful nonprofits, to some of the biggest names in the industry; such as Politico, Microsoft, Meta, Google, The New York Times Co., and The Nobel Prize Committee.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Intentionally remote since day one, spanning six continents and 38+ countries, 10up fully embraces the benefits of distributed work. Join our team of collaborative, cross-discipline professionals who have been working together to push the boundaries of enterprise-level projects and deliver white glove service to our partners for over 12 years.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
